tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE visas (
    visa_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    passport_number VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    visa_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    issue_date DATE NOT NULL,
    expiry_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE visa_information (
    visa_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(255),
    last_name VARCHAR(255),
    nationality VARCHAR(100),
    visa_type VARCHAR(100),
    entry_date DATE,
    expiration_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE passport_details (
    passport_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    full_name VARCHAR(255),
    nationality VARCHAR(100),
    passport_number VARCHAR(20),
    issue_date DATE,
    expiration_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE visa_information (
    visa_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visa_country VARCHAR(50),
    visa_type VARCHAR(50),
    visa_start_date DATE,
    visa_end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE passport_details (
    passport_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    passport_number VARCHAR(20),
    issue_date DATE,
    expiry_date DATE,
    nationality VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE travel_documents (
    document_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    document_name VARCHAR(50),
    document_type VARCHAR(50),
    document_number VARCHAR(20),
    issue_country VARCHAR(50),
    issue_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE passport_details ( 
    passport_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    user_id INT, 
    passport_number VARCHAR(20), 
    issuing_country VARCHAR(50), 
    expiry_date DATE 
);

CREATE TABLE travel_documents ( 
    document_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    user_id INT, 
    document_type VARCHAR(50), 
    document_number VARCHAR(20), 
    issuing_country VARCHAR(50), 
    expiry_date DATE 
);

CREATE TABLE visas (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  country VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  visa_type VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE passport_details (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  passport_number VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
  country_of_issue VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  issue_date DATE,
  expiry_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE travel_documents (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  document_type VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  document_number VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
  issue_date DATE,
  expiry_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE personal_details (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  full_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  date_of_birth DATE,
  nationality VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  email VARCHAR(255),
  phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE address_details (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  street_address VARCHAR(255),
  city VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  country VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  postal_code VARCHAR(10)
);
